Sentencas: The perovskite La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 (- delta) (LSCMMn0.30Ni0.20) was evaluated as potential electrode for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: The electrochemical performances of LSCMMn0.30Ni0.20 for hydrogen oxidation and oxygen reduction reactions were studied at 800 degrees C. Symmetrical cells LSCMMn0.30Ni0.20/YSZ/LSCMMn0.30Ni0.20 were studied by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: The total conductivity of LSCMMn0.30Ni0.20 is 22 S cm(-1) in air and 0.8 S cm(-1) under wet 5% H-2/Ar at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) at 800 degrees C for hydrogen oxidation reaction is 1 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: The ASR for oxygen reduction reaction is 1.6 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: An ageing study during 24 h shows a relatively good stability of the electrochemical performances.
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ

Sentencas: LSCMMn0.3Ni0.2 seems to be a promising dual electrode for a symmetrical SOFC.
Titulo: Electrochemical properties of novel SOFC dual electrode La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.3Ni0.2O3 - δ
